{"data":[{"date":"07:58 08/07","title":"Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup: L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu Harry n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ee9u b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Harry kh\u00e1c ra tay. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 10 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Harry Maguire s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng ai ng\u1edd t\u1edbi.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/275571/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\nV\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Harry Maguire ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o gia nh\u1eadp Leicester City sau khi c\u00f9ng Hull City xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1edd, trung v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1eaft x\u00edch ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Quay cu\u1ed3ng ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t l\u1eafm kh\u00f4ng Harry, khi anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1m b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n m\u1edbi h\u00f2 h\u1eb9n nhau ra qu\u1ea7y bar c\u1ed5 v\u0169 Tam S\u01b0 \u1edf Euro 2016 qua m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh TV?</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Harry-Maguire-tran-Anh-vs-Thuy-Dien-Nguoi-hung-bat-dac-di-Tam-Su-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire m\u1edbi hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t C\u0110V v\u00f4 danh theo ch\u00e2n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf Euro 2016</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> V\u1edbi b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Kyle Walker c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi John Stones d\u00e2ng cao l\u00ean khu trung tuy\u1ebfn, Southgate h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1n th\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean Gary Cahill v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u1eadn Tunisia ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai tu\u1ea7n.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Kh\u00f4ng, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 47 tu\u1ed5i thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Maguire v\u00f4 danh v\u00e0 non n\u1edbt \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u1ec7ch tr\u00e1i, gi\u1eb1ng x\u00e9 d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng lu\u1ed3ng tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t con ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00f4ng &ndash; d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m, li\u1ec1u l\u0129nh hay \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ngu ng\u1ed1c, r\u1ea5t ngu ng\u1ed1c. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf, canh b\u1ea1c \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Harry Kane \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp m\u1edf ra c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 28 n\u0103m cho n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Anh-vao-ban-ket-World-Cup-Lai-la-nguoi-hung-Harry,-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng vang trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y \u1edf Leicester City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> H\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 h\u1ed9 ph\u00e1p ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 (cao 1m95 v\u00e0 n\u1eb7ng 100kg) khi\u1ebfn Maguire c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111eo b\u00e1m, theo k\u00e8m trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean ch\u00ednh, kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua anh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n hay ho m\u00e0 k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u00e3nh di\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Tunisia, Panama r\u1ed3i Colombia, ba \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ba n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1c nhau, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 sau c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ch\u1ecbu ph\u1eadn n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a 7/9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-o-tran-colombia-vs-anh-nguoi-thu-linh-phot-tinh-ang-le-421-190324.html\" target=\"_blank\">g\u00e3 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh ph\u1edbt t\u1ec9nh &quot;\u0102ng-l\u00ea&quot; Harry Kane</span>, Maguire v\u00e0 Stones sau khi x\u1edbi tung nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 l\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-ra-quan-suon-se-niem-hy-vong-tu-2-chang-harry-421-188889.html\">\u0110T Anh ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb: Ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb hai ch\u00e0ng Harry</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">7 l\u00ean 8 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Maguire d\u00e1n m\u1eaft v\u00e0o tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng bay t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ashley Young \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i phi th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t t\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00fang \u0111i\u1ec3m giao c\u1eaft, cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u00e1o v\u00e0ng qu\u1ea7n xanh n\u00e0o, hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 full \u0111\u1ecf, n\u1eb1m \u0111o s\u00e0n n\u1ebfu d\u00e1m c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng lao m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c t\u00e0n ph\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111ong \u0111\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a anh.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">M\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh th\u1eb3ng b\u0103ng, Anh 1-0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, ph\u00fat 30, t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du am Anh vs Thuy Dien\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/lot-vao-ban-ket-nguoi-anh-bat-dau-mo-cup-vang.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edf ra c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m cho Tam S\u01b0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em><span style=\"color:#111111\"> &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00e1t khao v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i.&rdquo;</span></em><span style=\"color:#111111\"> &ndash; Chia s\u1ebb ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a Maguire sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11, v\u1ec1 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 tr\u1ebb trung \u0111ang dung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng anh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. C\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, trung v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Maguire gia nh\u1eadp Leicester v\u1edbi c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 12-17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 r\u1ebb \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00edt ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 danh, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn anh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ebfm hoi ch\u01a1i tr\u1ecdn 38 tr\u1eadn Premier League cho B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf King Power.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cau-chuyen-ve-harry-maguire-nguoi-hung-nhu-buoc-ra-tu-tro-choi-gia-lap-465-190649.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/cau-chuyen-ve-harry-maguire-nguoi-hung-nhu-buoc-ra-tu-tro-choi-gia-lap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cau-chuyen-ve-harry-maguire-nguoi-hung-nhu-buoc-ra-tu-tro-choi-gia-lap-465-190649.html\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 Harry Maguire: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ra t\u1eeb tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i gi\u1ea3 l\u1eadp</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Harry Maguire t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng hai Anh \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh trong tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed v\u1eady.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">V\u1eady m\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0ng ho\u00e0ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh trung v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 kho\u1ea3ng hai th\u00e1ng, Maguire ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 trong chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn London v\u00e0 ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi n\u0103m b\u00e0n thua tr\u1eafng l\u00e0m qu\u00e0 t\u1eeb Crystal Palace.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">\u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-anh-vs-thuy-dien-421-190634.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span> bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n khi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 co c\u1ee5m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n b\u1edfi Maguire, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gieo r\u1eafc \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng cho Marcus Berg t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Maguire, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i anh v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t &ndash; s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb, th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng hay tinh th\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Maguire tran Anh vs Thuy Dien\" title=\"Harry Maguire tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, ch\u1ee9ng minh cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> Nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea5p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf lu\u00f4n tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00fang ki\u1ec3u &ldquo;kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u chui l\u00ean&rdquo; nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u1ed1c n\u00e0o trong n\u0103m nay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n c\u00e1i v\u01b0\u01a1n m\u00ecnh b\u01b0\u1edbc ra \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Maguire. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i cu\u1ed9c so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tam S\u01b0, gi\u1edd trung v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp to\u00e0n h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup, \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau 28 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Italia 90 &ndash; m\u1ecdi th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eafc ghi c\u00f4ng danh cho Harry Maguire.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, trung v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Leicester s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 trong v\u00f2ng h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2><strong>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018:</strong><strong><br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky-421-190646.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky-421-190646.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7?</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n mang \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0, \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1017","checkdouble":"190658"},{"date":"07:34 08/07","title":"B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng, Suarez h\u1eb1n h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1 Griezmann \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/bi-loai-cay-dang-suarez-han-hoc-to-griezmann-dao-duc-gia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luis Suarez nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-0 Uruguay khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao Barcelona tan m\u1ed9ng World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/du-am-uruguay-vs-phap-02-sai-lam-nhung-khoanh-khac-va-giot-nuoc-mat-nghen-ngao-421-190576.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p h\u1ea1 Uruguay \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span> \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Raphael Varane v\u00e0 Antoine Griezmann. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9, ng\u00f4i sao Atletico Madrid ch\u1ec9 l\u1eb3ng l\u1eb7ng quay v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7u nh\u1ea3y h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luis Suarez t\u1ed1 Griezmann \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3 v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luis Suarez t\u1ed1 Griezmann \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3 v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/bi-loai-cay-dang-suarez-han-hoc-to-griezmann-dao-duc-gia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luis Suarez t\u1ed1 Griezmann \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3 sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-0 Uruguay t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">M\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u00fd do xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t may m\u1eafn khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Fernando Muslera m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1eaft d\u00ednh b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eb1ng sau nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Griezmann quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 anh m\u1edbi gi\u00e3i b\u00e0y:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 vui v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh World Cup. Th\u1ef1c ra, t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i bu\u1ed3n h\u01a1n v\u00ec c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Atleti c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn (Diego Godin v\u00e0 Jose Gimenez). T\u00f4i v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi con ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 v\u0103n h\u00f3a Uruguay, v\u1eady n\u00ean c\u1ea3m x\u00fac khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">\u201cB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.\u201d - Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Griezmann th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-griezmann-truoc-tran-phap-vs-uruguay-421-190375.html\" target=\"_blank\">\"m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay\u201d</span>, coi \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Nam M\u1ef9 nh\u01b0 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Griezmann ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec c\u00e1i t\u00e1t v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t Luis Suarez. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-0 Uruguay \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Barcelona th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1eb1n h\u1ecdc \u00e1m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ecf v\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3, n\u00f3i:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">\u201cGriezmann kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u0111\u00e2u. C\u1eadu ta l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n lo\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u1eadu ta \u0111\u00e2u c\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3cth\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ed1 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay nh\u01b0ng xin l\u1ed7i, ch\u00fang ta r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nhau.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-quet-sach-nam-my-thien-bien-van-hoa-voi-hai-bo-mat-421-190609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/phap-quet-sach-nam-my-thien-bien-van-hoa-voi-hai-bo-mat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-quet-sach-nam-my-thien-bien-van-hoa-voi-hai-bo-mat-421-190609.html\">Ph\u00e1p qu\u00e9t s\u1ea1ch Nam M\u1ef9: Thi\u00ean bi\u1ebfn v\u1ea1n h\u00f3a v\u1edbi hai b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t</span><br>\r\nPeru, Argentina v\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n Uruguay m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1016","checkdouble":"190662"},{"date":"07:36 08/07","title":"B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Man Utd \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh m\u00e0 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 \u0111ang th\u1eafng l\u1edbn khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n 50 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 \u1edf Premier League.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh th\u1eafng th\u1ebf<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 92 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 41 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League (chi\u1ebfm t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 44.56%). Con s\u1ed1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du am Anh vs Thuy Dien\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 41 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Anh g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9ng sau Anh l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p (Ligue 1) v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (La Liga) v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 12 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. C\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c, Italia (7), B\u1ec9, Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Croatia (2), Scotland, \u00c1o, Nga, Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 Ukraine (1).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong n\u01b0\u1edbc (Ligue 1 - t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 39.1%) v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Anh, chi\u1ebfm 21.7%. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Croatia c\u00f2n th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 12 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh. Croatia c\u00f3 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i Anh l\u00e0 Dejan Lovren (Liverpool).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 41 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Anh g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi c\u00e1c CLB \u1edf Premier League s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y nh\u1ea5t. D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 Tottenham v\u1edbi 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed3m Harry Kane, Dele Alli, Eric Dier, Trippier, Danny Rose (Anh), Alderweireld, Vertonghen, Mousa Dembele (B\u1ec9), Hugo Lloris (Ph\u00e1p).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBa \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng sau l\u00e0 Chelsea, Man Utd v\u00e0 Man City v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 7 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u00e0 Liverpool (4), Leicester (2), Arsenal, Everton, Burnley, Stoke v\u00e0 West Brom (1).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o khung 1h00 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (11/7) v\u00e0 Croatia vs Anh (12/7).<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/croatia-vao-ban-ket-dejan-lovren-khen-dt-nga-465-190657.html\">Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Dejan Lovren b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-croatia-kich-tinh-nhu-phim-465-190652.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia: K\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 phim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien-465-190650.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn, Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll v\u00ec l\u1ee1 d\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-mu-tuyen-anh-di-len-tu-tuyet-vong-thanh-tuyet-voi-421-190648.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU: Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111i l\u00ean t\u1eeb tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng th\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lot-vao-ban-ket-nguoi-anh-bat-dau-mo-cup-vang-421-190647.html\">L\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u01a1 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky-421-190646.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1015","checkdouble":"190664"},{"date":"07:20 08/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (8/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u0